{
  "comment": "$$x^2\\log_{2^9}(x+5)\\leq \\log_2(x+5)^2\\\\ \\frac{x^2}{9}\\log_2(x+5)\\leq 2\\log_2|x+5|\\\\ x>-5\\\\ \\frac{x^2}{9}\\log_2(x+5)\\leq 2\\log_2(x+5)\\\\ \\frac{x^2}{9}\\log_2(x+5)-2\\log_2(x+5)\\leq 0\\\\ \\log_2(x+5)(\\frac{x^2}{9}-2)\\leq 0\\\\ \\log_2(x-5)=0\\Rightarrow x=-4\\\\ \\frac{x^2}{9}-2=0\\Rightarrow x^2=18\\Rightarrow x=\\pm 3\\sqrt{2},т.к.~x>-5\\\\ x\\in (-5;-3\\sqrt{2}]\\cup [-4;3\\sqrt{2}]$$\nОтвет: \\(x\\in ( -5;-3\\sqrt{2}] \\cup [ -4;3\\sqrt{2}]\\).",
